results.name: Number of normal semistandard Young tableaux whose shape is the conjugate of the integer partition with Heinz number n.
comment: A tableau is normal if its entries span an initial interval of positive integers. The Heinz number of an integer partition (y_1,...,y_k) is prime(y_1)*...*prime(y_k).
results.author: _Gus Wiseman_, Feb 15 2018
